description: Java class representing the response body for ToDo item data, including fields such as id, title, description, completion status, due date, creation time, and update time.

classes.name: ToDoResponse
classes.description: Data transfer object (DTO) for returning ToDo item details in API responses.

methods.name: getId
methods.description: Returns the id of the ToDo item.

methods.name: setId
methods.description: Sets the id of the ToDo item.

methods.name: getTitle
methods.description: Returns the title of the ToDo item.

methods.name: setTitle
methods.description: Sets the title of the ToDo item.

methods.name: getDescription
methods.description: Returns the description of the ToDo item.

methods.name: setDescription
methods.description: Sets the description of the ToDo item.

methods.name: isCompleted
methods.description: Returns whether the ToDo item is completed.

methods.name: setCompleted
methods.description: Sets the completed status of the ToDo item.

methods.name: getDueDate
methods.description: Returns the due date of the ToDo item.

methods.name: setDueDate
methods.description: Sets the due date of the ToDo item.

methods.name: getCreatedAt
methods.description: Returns the creation timestamp of the ToDo item.

methods.name: setCreatedAt
methods.description: Sets the creation timestamp of the ToDo item.

methods.name: getUpdatedAt
methods.description: Returns the last update timestamp of the ToDo item.

methods.name: setUpdatedAt
methods.description: Sets the last update timestamp of the ToDo item.
